      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk it feels different tho. the signal strength literally changes depending on which room i'm in. like if i go to my kitchen it gets way stronger and when im in the bedroom it dips. if it was just some random guy's router why would it be so sensitive to where i'm standing in my house??",
